ading `TZDIR` on each\ncall so that runtime changes are reflected immediately.\n","docLink":"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.html#Std.Time.Database.TZdb.getZoneRules","kind":"def","line":168,"name":"Std.Time.Database.TZdb.getZoneRules","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.lean#L168-L177"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.html#Std.Time.Database.TZdb.getLocalZoneRules\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Time</span>.<span class=\"name\">Database</span>.<span class=\"name\">TZdb</span>.<span class=\"name\">getLocalZoneRules</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">db</span> : <a href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.html#Std.Time.Database.TZdb\">TZdb</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/System/IO.html#IO\">IO</a> <a href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/ZoneRules.html#Std.Time.TimeZone.ZoneRules\">TimeZone.ZoneRules</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Retrieves the timezone rules for the local timezone, re-reading the `TZ` and `TZDIR`\nenvironment variables on each call so that runtime changes are reflected immediately.\n","docLink":"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.html#Std.Time.Database.TZdb.getLocalZoneRules","kind":"def","line":160,"name":"Std.Time.Database.TZdb.getLocalZoneRules","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.lean#L160-L166"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.html#Std.Time.Database.TZdb.resolveZonesPaths\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Time</span>.<span class=\"name\">Database</span>.<span class=\"name\">TZdb</span>.<span class=\"name\">resolveZonesPaths</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">db</span> : <a href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.html#Std.Time.Database.TZdb\">TZdb</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/System/IO.html#IO\">IO</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/System/FilePath.html#System.FilePath\">System.FilePath</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Builds the effective zoneinfo search path by prepending the current `TZDIR` (if set and\nexists on disk) to `db.zonesPaths`. Called on every lookup so that runtime changes to\n`TZDIR` are reflected immediately.\n","docLink":"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.html#Std.Time.Database.TZdb.resolveZonesPaths","kind":"def","line":148,"name":"Std.Time.Database.TZdb.resolveZonesPaths","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.lean#L148-L158"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.html#Std.Time.Database.TZdb.default\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Time</span>.<span class=\"name\">Database</span>.<span class=\"name\">TZdb</span>.<span class=\"name\">default</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.html#Std.Time.Database.TZdb\">TZdb</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Returns a `TZdb` with common fallback zoneinfo paths for Linux and macOS.\nCall this once at program startup. The `TZ` and `TZDIR` environment variables\nare re-read on every `getLocalZoneRules`/`getZoneRules` call, so runtime changes\nto those variables are always reflected.\n","docLink":"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.html#Std.Time.Database.TZdb.default","kind":"def","line":139,"name":"Std.Time.Database.TZdb.default","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.lean#L139-L146"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.html#Std.Time.Database.TZdb.resolveLocalPath\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Time</span>.<span class=\"name\">Database</span>.<span class=\"name\">TZdb</span>.<span class=\"name\">resolveLocalPath</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">zonesPaths</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/System/FilePath.html#System.FilePath\">System.FilePath</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/System/IO.html#IO\">IO</a> <a href=\"./Init/System/FilePath.html#System.FilePath\">System.FilePath</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Resolves the local timezone file path from the `TZ` environment variable, searching\n`zonesPaths` for relative paths and timezone IDs. Falls back to `/etc/localtime` if\n`TZ` is unset. Throws if `TZ` is set but its value cannot be found on disk.\n","docLink":"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.html#Std.Time.Database.TZdb.resolveLocalPath","kind":"def","line":118,"name":"Std.Time.Database.TZdb.resolveLocalPath","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.lean#L118-L137"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.html#Std.Time.Database.TZdb.findInPaths\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Time</span>.<span class=\"name\">Database</span>.<span 