` environment variable. Returns `none` for empty or\n`:` (empty path after the colon) values.\n","docLink":"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.html#Std.Time.Database.TZdb.parseTZValue","kind":"def","line":94,"name":"Std.Time.Database.TZdb.parseTZValue","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.lean#L94-L105"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.html#Std.Time.Database.TZdb.instBEqTZSpec.beq\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Time</span>.<span class=\"name\">Database</span>.<span class=\"name\">TZdb</span>.<span class=\"name\">instBEqTZSpec</span>.<span class=\"name\">beq</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.html#Std.Time.Database.TZdb.TZSpec\">TZSpec</a> → <a href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.html#Std.Time.Database.TZdb.TZSpec\">TZSpec</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.html#Std.Time.Database.TZdb.instBEqTZSpec.beq","kind":"def","line":92,"name":"Std.Time.Database.TZdb.instBEqTZSpec.beq","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.lean#L92-L92"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/TZdb.html#Std.Time.Database.TZdb.instBEqTZSpec\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Time</span>.<span class=\"name\">Database</span>.<span class=\"name\">TZdb</span>.<span class=\"name\">instBEqTZSpec</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq<